<P>
Analysts say this indicates that China is gaining popularity
among foreign tourism agencies.
</P>
<P>
The Guangzhou tourism expo was launched in 1993, and is viewed
as a window for China's tourism industry. Nearly 300 tourism
businesses attended the latest show, with overseas businesses
getting the spotlight.
