commercial agencies took an active part in the exhibition.
</P>
<P>
It also was the first time for the five ASEAN nations to show
up at the exhibition as a team.
</P>
<P>
Last year, China's tourism industry reported foreign currency
earnings amounting to ten billion US dollars, up by 15 percent
over that of two years ago. The income for the industry from
domestic tourists was 160 billion yuan, up by 16 percent. 
