<P>
MEXICO CITY, March 2 (Xinhua) -- The United States and Jamaica
played to a 0-0 tie Sunday in a CONCACAF region World Cup
qualifying soccer match at the National Stadium in Kingston,
Jamaica.
</P>
<P>
The match was the first for both nations in the final round of
qualification for the 1998 World Cup in France.
</P>
