Brian McBride's header on Eric Wynalda's cross was deflected by
goalkeeper Warren Barrett.
</P>
<P>
The Jamaicans had a trio of corner kicks in the dying minutes
of the match, but were all spoiled by Keller, who parried a
Williams corner over the bar and followed by making a diving
clearance on a corner by Gregory Messam. 
